it through the previous rounds,

01:50.350 --> 01:54.490
along with your counterparts
in New York City, Los Angeles,

01:54.490 --> 01:59.290
and Chicago, where I add, the
competition is substantial.

01:59.290 --> 02:01.390
Your quest to beat
the world record

02:01.390 --> 02:06.940
of 360 words per minute, held
by Mark Kislingbury, begins.

02:06.940 --> 02:08.335
Open your stenos, please.

02:11.290 --> 02:15.670
This document has a
total of 361 words.

02:15.670 --> 02:19.360
You have 60 seconds
beginning now.

02:19.360 --> 02:23.440
Atlanta, Supreme Court, the
people of Georgia versus Steven

02:23.440 --> 02:25.840
Earl Brown charged with
two counts of arson,

02:25.840 --> 02:27.760
resulting in the
destruction of property

02:27.760 --> 02:30.700
