stands before this court

02:47.230 --> 02:49.300
in appeal of said charges.

02:49.300 --> 02:53.110
The people of Georgia have
submitted all evidence along

02:53.110 --> 02:54.836
with first hand
witness statements

02:54.836 --> 02:58.710
and expect the court to decide.

02:58.710 --> 02:59.510
Time.

03:04.040 --> 03:10.892
343, Ms. Kindleman.

03:10.892 --> 03:11.692
Mm.

03:22.580 --> 03:24.080
Hey, Walden.

03:24.080 --> 03:25.400
How did you do?

03:25.400 --> 03:27.400
Did you win the competition?

03:27.400 --> 03:30.110
Well, there's more
rounds to go, George.

03:30.110 --> 03:31.760
You forgot your
change, George.

03:31.760 --> 03:32.820
You want your usual soda?

03:32.820 --> 03:33.870
Oh, no.
Thanks, Daisy.

03:33.870 --> 03:34.670
I'm good.

03:34.670 --> 03:37.070
I was going a little
too hard on the pop.

03:37.070 --> 03:38.780
And those goblets
of carbonation are

03:38.780 --> 03:41.170
just pure calories and sugar.

03:41.170 --> 03:42.212
Nah, you look handsome.

03:42.212 --> 03:43.012
Oh, no.

03:43.012 --> 03:44.790
Don't you go getting
any ideas now, Daisy?

03:44.790 --> 03:45.590
Oh.

03:45.590 --> 03:46.650
Thank you, Daisy.

03:46.650 --> 03:47.450
You're welcome.

03:47.450 --> 03:48.380
Bye, Daisy.

03:48.380 --> 03:49.430
Bye!

03:49.430 --> 03:52.340
You know, the record's 360.

03:52.340 --> 03:54.920
How many words did
you manage, Walden?

03:54.920 --> 03:56.090
343.

03:56.090 --> 03:59.340
I'm going to be late
for court, George.

03:59.340 --> 04:02.100
That's only 17 less.

04:02.100 --> 04:05.010
You won't like today's case.

04:05.010 --> 04:07.650
Bad man.

04:07.650 --> 04:09.285
Very bad man!

04:13.730 --> 04:15.230
VAN DRIES: We are
living in a world

04:15.230 --> 04:18.329
where we coexist
with evil as a norm.

04:18.329 --> 04:19.800
Objection, Your Honor.

04:19.800 --> 04:21.640
Don't object during
closing, Lloyd.

04:21.640 --> 04:22.440
It's rude.

04:26.160 --> 04:27.660
Miss Van Dries.

04:27.660 --> 04:28.860
Thank you, Your Honor.

04:31.560 --> 04:36.280
So when do we start
to punish such evil?

04:36.280 --> 04:42.790
The pendulum must swing back to
some form of sanity, morality,

04:42.790 --> 04:47.850
just downright goodness.

04:47.850 --> 04:52.380
Norman Casey Bolt,
high on crack cocaine,

04:52.380 --> 04:58.360
put his little three-year-old
daughter, Carmen,

04:58.360 --> 05:05.660
into his oven, locked her in,
and cooked her into her body

05:05.660 --> 05:13.580
was burned to the bone, for
washing her doll's hair.

05:13.580 --> 05:16.670
We, the people in the
great state of Georgia,

05:16.670 --> 05:21.830
reintroduced the death
penalty for one purpose only,

05:21.830 --> 05:25.490
to rid society of pure evil.

05:29.190 --> 05:35.790
Do you really want to send this
monster to a cot bed satellite

05:35.790 --> 05:41.640
TV and three meals a day?

05:41.640 --> 05:44.608
[CHATTERS]

05:45.410 --> 05:46.295
Thank you, Your Honor.

06:14.800 --> 06:16.225
The defendant please stand.

06:19.670 --> 06:23.660
Norman Casey Bolt, you have
been found guilty of the charge

06:23.660 --> 06:25.520
of murder in the first degree.

06:25.520 --> 06:28.280
This jury recommends
that you be given

06:28.280 --> 06:31.660
the harshest sentence possible.

06:31.660 --> 06:35.305
And given the heinous nature
of your crime, I concur.

06:41.930 --> 06:46.460
Mr. Bolt, what is inside
a man that would make him

06:46.460 --> 06:47.345
want to harm a child?

06:50.720 --> 06:52.430
Your life will be
terminated at a date

06:52.430 --> 06:54.958
to be determined by this court.

06:54.958 --> 06:58.346
NORMAN: [LAUGHS]

07:00.282 --> 07:02.230
[OVERLAPPING SPEECH]

07:02.230 --> 07:03.815
Halle- fucking- lujah.

07:06.770 --> 07:08.047
Motherfuck--

07:08.047 --> 07:09.041
PEOPLE: Oh.

07:09.041 --> 07:11.253
[GASPS]

07:11.253 --> 07:12.670
JUDGE BOYLE: Clyde,
get this piece

07:12.670 --> 07:14.868
of garbage out of my courtroom.

07:14.868 --> 07:19.510
NORMAN: [CHUCKLES]
This ain't over.

07:19.510 --> 07:21.250
[EXHALES]

07:21.250 --> 07:26.510
JUDGE BOYLE: Walden, lunch?

07:26.510 --> 07:28.195
