07:28.195 --> 07:28.995
You all right?

07:28.995 --> 07:31.520
Hey, I am fine.

07:31.520 --> 07:35.160
I hear that junkie son of
a bitch was found guilty.

07:35.160 --> 07:35.960
Yep.

07:35.960 --> 07:37.850
Oh, that poor little girl.

07:37.850 --> 07:41.780
She's come in here, all
bruised and beaten up,

07:41.780 --> 07:43.790
