01:00:22.870 --> 01:00:23.670
BILL: Yes.

01:00:23.670 --> 01:00:25.018
You got to Mirandize him.

01:00:25.018 --> 01:00:26.310
Billy, you got him Mirandized--

01:00:26.310 --> 01:00:29.310
