01:04:05.460 --> 01:04:06.260
What?

01:04:06.260 --> 01:04:08.478
Local retard can
have an evil streak?

01:04:08.478 --> 01:04:09.954
I mean, what the fuck
is it to you, Walden?

01:04:09.954 --> 01:04:10.756
OK.

01:04:10.756 --> 01:04:11.940
I just don't
believe George would

01:04:11.940 --> 01:04:14.130
